<promed@promedmail.org>

[Chikungunya virus is endemic in Southeast Asia, including Myanmar.
This report provides no information supporting the statement that the
virus came into Myanmar from Thailand. Chikungunya virus infections
in Myanmar were reported earlier this year (2010), and the outbreak
apparently has continued.

A map of Myanmar showing the administrative divisions can be accessed at
<http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/middle_east_and_asia/burma_pol_96.jpg>.
A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map for Myanmar and neighboring
countries can be accessed at
<http://healthmap.org/r/008a>. - Mod.TY]

